printer_notes.1.4.4:
Dont remove the following keywords! These keywords are used in the "compatible printer" condition of the print and filament profiles to link the particular print and filament profiles to this printer profile.
PRINTER_VENDOR_MAKERGEAR
PRINTER_MODEL_MAKERGEAR_U1_DUPLICATION

end_gcode.1.4.4:
M106 P2 S0 ; turn off exhaust fan

M104 S0 ; turn off extruder
M104 S0 T0 ; turn off extruder
M104 S0 T1; turn off extruder
M104 S0 T2; turn off extruder
M140 P0 S0 ; turn off bed
M140 P1 S0 ; turn off bed
M140 P2 S0 ; turn off bed
M140 P3 S0 ; turn off bed
M106 S0 ; turn off cooling fan
G91 ; relative mode
G1 Z20 ; move Z down 20mm
G90;  absolute mode

G28 XY ; home tool/s
M502 ; set to firmware default values
T0 ; defualt tool should always be T0

start_gcode.1.4.4:
;U1 Rev0 Duplication Script - T0 and T1

M203 X18000.00 Y18000.00 Z1200.00 U18000.00 E1800.00 ; U1 max feedrate mm/minute
        M201 X1000 Y1000 Z10 U1000 E2000                    ; U1 Maximum Acceleration axes mm/s^2
        M204 P2000 T2000           ; U1 Maximum Acceleration printing / travel mm/s^2
        M566 X300 Y300 Z60 U300 E600 ; U1  instantenous speed change 'jerk' in mm/minute
        M593 F0                     ;make sure dynamix acceleration is off 


; turn off T0 hot end to reduce ooze on the bed during startup. NOTE: this does not explicitly wait for the hotends to totally cool down
M104 T0 S0
M104 T1 S0
M104 T2 S0


M221 D0 S100 ;extruder rate for T0 is set in S3D so set to 100% here
M221 D1 S100 ;extruder rate for T1 is set in S3D so set to 100% here


M140 P0 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]				;Middle bed heater strip
M140 P1 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]				;2nd from left and second from right bed heater
M140 P2 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]				;Left bed heater strip
M140 P3 S[first_layer_bed_temperature]				;Right bed heater strip

M116 ; wait for all bed heaters to get to temp before probing. This will wait for cooldown if there is overshoot. 

G29 S2 ; Clear any meshes 
G28 XY; home XY
G28 Z ;Home Z
G32    ;Auto Level 
G28 Z ; rehome Z

;Get hot ends up to temp
M104 T0 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}
M104 T1 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}
M104 T2 S{first_layer_temperature[0]}
M116 ; wait for all bed heaters to get to temp before probing. This will wait for cooldown if there is overshoot. 


;***Initial Purge***
T2
G1 Z20.0 F6000             ; Move Z to 20

G92 E0                     ; Zero Extruder

M564 S0 ; safteys off
G1 X160 Y5F10000; move to unused front edge
G1 Z0.30 F1000
G1 X40 E20 F1000
G1 X30 Z0.05 F1000 ; wipe off tail
G1 Z10
G1 Y11 ;safe zone
G92 E0

M564 S0 ; safteys off


M106 P2 S100; exhaust fan change S value to enable (50 is a good starting value)

; end startup script
